Sunglasses 😎are far more than just a practical accessory to protect your eyes from the sun. 🔆
They’re also a fashion statement and a reflection of your personality that can enhance or detract from your professional image. Here are the do’s and don’ts of proper sunglasses etiquette.😊

📌Don’ts

❌ Sunglasses should not be kept on top of your head 
Sunglasses are Not a hair Accessory Oftentimes, people put shades on their head while they are shopping or running errand.
❌ Wearing your sunglasses while attending a business meeting or talking to someone casually.
❌Don't throw your shades in your purse or bag.

📌Do’s

✅ Take off your sunglasses while talking with someone ,it is appropriate to remove your sunglass, Know that looking at the eyes of the person you are talking to is an integral part of excellent communication. 

✅ Sunglasses should be worn on eyes or the other action you could take is to fold them and put them into the specified container.

✅Always use a case
Think about all the random things in our purses/bags. Your sunglasses will thank you later for always keeping them in their cases OR a microfiber pouch.
